'''Dagon'hai robes''' are a set of magic robes worn by members of the [[Dagon'hai]], an ancient [[Zamorak]]ian organisation. Obtained from [[Larran's big chest]] at a rate of 1/256 per piece, they require level 70 [[Magic]] and 40 [[Defence]] to wear. It can be stored in a [[magic wardrobe]] in a player owned house.

These robes are [[Zamorak#Affiliated items|Zamorak affiliated items]], including when worn in the [[God Wars Dungeon]].

